00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:22,460
 Hong Kong is our home.

423
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:26,740
 Its people are our family.

424
00:26:26,740 --> 00:26:32,860
 If we were to begin each day with a short prayer

425
00:26:32,860 --> 00:26:35,700
 to bless Hong Kong, bless its people,

426
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:37,400
 and oh yes, bless the vine.

