00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:42,260
 And bless every other church in our city as well

428
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:43,180
 at the same time.

429
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:48,900
 I believe that we would very soon see a change

430
00:26:48,900 --> 00:26:51,120
 in the spiritual atmosphere here.

