00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:56,120
 Dr. Ed Silvozo, a friend of mine,

432
00:26:56,120 --> 00:27:00,760
 in his excellent book, "Prayer Evangelism,"

433
00:27:00,760 --> 00:27:03,200
 how to change the spiritual climate

