00:27:13,620 --> 00:27:17,760
 He says this, "Number one, bless them.

438
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:21,580
 "Number two, fellowship with them.

439
00:27:21,580 --> 00:27:26,220
 "Number three, take care of their needs.

440
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:29,860
 "And then, at the bottom of the pile,

441
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:31,800
 "proclaim the good news."

442
00:27:31,800 --> 00:27:38,820
 Step one is blessing.

443
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:42,080
 Dr. Ed describes it as speaking peace to them.

444
00:27:42,080 --> 00:27:48,680
 He says, "Bless, befriend, care, share,

445
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:53,240
 "bless, befriend, care, share."

446
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:57,000
 How often do churches do it the other way around?

