00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:09,280
 So what I'm proposing in line with my three points,

480
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:11,600
 all good sermons have three points,

481
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:15,240
 is this, in a moment we're gonna pray a prayer

